GetRewardConcreteUnitTest
├── When the caller is not the token owner
│   └── It should revert with {NA}
└── When the caller is the token owner
    ├── When there are no accrued rewards
    │   └── It should not transfer any tokens
    └── When there are accrued rewards
        ├── When penalty rate is zero
        │   ├── It should transfer full rewards to owner
        │   └── It should emit a {ClaimRewards} event
        └── When penalty rate is greater than zero
            ├── When called within min stake time
            │   ├── When penalty rounds down to zero
            │   │   └── It should transfer full rewards to owner
            │   └── When penalty does not round down to zero
            │       ├── When there are no remaining rewards after penalty
            │       │   ├── It should transfer penalty to minter
            │       │   └── It should emit a {EarlyWithdrawPenalty} event
            │       └── When there are remaining rewards after penalty
            │           ├── It should transfer penalty to minter
            │           ├── It should emit a {EarlyWithdrawPenalty} event
            │           ├── It should transfer remaining rewards to owner
            │           └── It should emit a {ClaimRewards} event
            └── When called after min stake time
                ├── It should transfer full rewards to owner
                └── It should emit a {ClaimRewards} event
